label.phrase: but i can certainly help her reach one of the goals she had before she died to make sure chasing rainbows reaches young adults throughout bc canada the us and the rest of the world our hope sara's and mine has always been that the film can be used to raise public awareness of the unique challenges facing young adults living with cancer they need help to address their needs which are not only medical but also financial logistical and emotional both in the short and long term i will continue to do what i can to make that happen
